msgctxt "#31506"
msgid "Current built-in revision level of the default Madnox values to reset / initialize the skin."
msgstr "Trenutna vgrajena različica privzetih vrednosti Madnox za ponastavitev / inicializacijo preobleke."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31507"
msgid "Select if an intro video will play when Kodi is first started. None: No video, Built-In: Kodi's release level intro video, Custom: Pick video of your choice to display."
msgstr "Izberite, ali naj se ob prvem zagonu Kodija predvaja uvodni video. Brez: Brez videa, Vgrajen: Uvodni video različice Kodi, Po meri: Izberite poljuben video za prikaz."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31508"
msgid "This setting forces the media flag to resolution flag as 4K or 2160p providing user icon control without skin modifcations."
msgstr "Ta nastavitev prisili medijsko zastavico na ločljivost 4K ali 2160p, kar omogoča nadzor nad ikonami uporabnika brez spreminjanja preobleke."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31509"
msgid "Change the stars color displayed in the video info line. Click to cycle through fixed colors or select a custom color."
msgstr "Spremenite barvo zvezdic, prikazanih v vrstici z informacijami o videu. Kliknite za kroženje med določenimi barvami ali izberite barvo po meri."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31510"
msgid "Allows star ratings style to use a custom color when it is set to \"Custom\"."
msgstr "Omogoča, da slog ocenjevanja z zvezdicami uporablja barvo po meri, ko je nastavljen na \"Po meri\"."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31511"
msgid "Dedicated addon for Madnox required for Piers+. Moves all free running scripts to a dedicated addon for security purposes."
msgstr "Namenski dodatek za Madnox, potreben za Piers+. Premakne vse prosto delujoče skripte v namenski dodatek zaradi varnosti."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31512"
msgid "TMDbHelper provides several tools to assist skinners with retrieving information from TMDb, OMDb and Trakt APIs."
msgstr "TMDbHelper ponuja več orodij, ki oblikovalcem preoblek pomagajo pri pridobivanju informacij iz vmesnikov TMDb, OMDb in Trakt API."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31513"
msgid "Wikipedia addon for Kodi."
msgstr "Dodatek Wikipedia za Kodi."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31514"
msgid "Advanced CinemaVision replacement that can be enabled to replace Madnox's built in simpler CinemaMode. Allows the ultimate CinemaMode experience and customisation."
msgstr "Napredna zamenjava za CinemaVision, ki jo je mogoče omogočiti za zamenjavo vgrajenega preprostega načina CinemaMode v Madnoxu. Omogoča vrhunsko izkušnjo in prilagajanje kino načina."

#: /16x9/Includes_CustomSelect.xml
msgctxt "#31515"
msgid "Blur with color"
msgstr "Zamegli z barvo"

