#: Custom_1109_DialogConfirmExtrasInstall.xml
msgctxt "#31520"
msgid "This will re-run the optional extras installer. All extras will be downloaded and installed in a disabled state. Enable only what you need in Settings > Skin Settings > Addons."
msgstr "To bo ponovno zagnalo namestitveni program za neobvezne dodatke. Vsi dodatki bodo preneseni in nameščeni v onemogočenem stanju. Omogočite samo tisto, kar potrebujete v Nastavitve > Nastavitve preobleke > Dodatki."

