msgstr "Prikaži ocene kot 10-točkovna števila"

#: /16x9/SkinSettings.xml
msgctxt "#31524"
msgid "Allows changes to the ratings to convert between floating numbers or as a percentage. Affects TMDb & IMDb, all others remain as their default display."
msgstr "Omogoča pretvorbo ocen med decimalnimi števili ali odstotki. Vpliva na TMDb in IMDb, medtem ko vsi ostali ostanejo na privzetem prikazu."

#: /16x9/SkinSettings.xml
msgctxt "#31525"
msgid "Re-run skin shortcuts migrator"
msgstr "Ponovno zaženi selitev bližnjic preobleke"

#: /16x9/SkinSettings.xml
msgctxt "#31526"
msgid "This will rewrite the skin shortcuts .properties file to the current 3 module addon structure. Only run if there are issues with background images or playlists are not working."
msgstr "To bo prepisalo datoteko .properties bližnjic preobleke v trenutno strukturo dodatkov s 3 moduli. Zaženite le, če so težave z ozadji ali če seznami predvajanja ne delujejo."

#: /16x9/SkinSettings.xml
msgctxt "#31527"
msgid "This will reactivate the addons installer. Only run if addons were not installed when skin was first installed."
msgstr "To bo ponovno aktiviralo namestitveni program za dodatke. Zaženite le, če dodatki niso bili nameščeni ob prvi namestitvi preobleke."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
